# Professional Course Protection
# 1. Explicitly allow the Dashboard and Intro (with and without trailing slashes)
/course/dashboard     /course/dashboard/index.html  200
/course/dashboard/    /course/dashboard/index.html  200
/course/01-introduction   /course/01-introduction/index.html  200
/course/01-introduction/  /course/01-introduction/index.html  200

# 2. Protect everything else in /course/ for 'paid' users only
/course/*  200!  Role=paid

# 3. Redirect unauthorized users back to the dashboard
/course/*  /course/dashboard/  302!
